item.title: How do get my server on to the sever status
item.dc:creator: @moh moh
item.description:
@moh wrote:

You see this :
Last updated 17.28 minutes ago, next update in (When this is like 1/2 min register it)12.72 minutes.
Click here to register your own server.
This keeps servers in the database until their uptime drops below 40%.
Show Offline Servers

When Next update is in like 1/2 min register your server because then it shows your server in the page .
